description: Your next smart move in South Boston! Updated two bedroom and one bath condo in a professionally managed, pet-friendly building with one deeded space in a heated garage, indoor bike storage, shared yard and laundry in building. Nearly 850 sq. ft. of open-concept living with hardwood floors, 12-ft ceilings and oversized windows that fill the space with natural light. Kitchen features white shaker cabinets, granite counters, and stainless appliances. Renovated bath offers boutique-hotel style with designer tile and sleek glass shower. Two spacious bedrooms with custom closet built-ins plus a bonus loft for guests! Unbeatable location with a Walk/Bike Score of 95—steps to Lincoln Tavern, Capo, Loco, Stats, Publico, M Street Beach, Castle Island and parks. Minutes to Whole Foods, Stop & Shop, Red Line (Broadway & Andrew Sq.), major bus routes, I-93, Seaport and Logan Airport. Ideal for an owner-occupant or investor in one of Boston’s hottest neighborhoods with strong rental demand!
